    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 features the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, delivering linear power delivery up to a soaring 8,400 RPM redline. Mated to a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable differential lock, this chassis provides exceptional analog feedback. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, ensuring the high-revving valvetrain remains robust. The suspension retains its composure with Electronic Damping Control (EDC) functioning across all modes. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical synchronization of the individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS system remains impeccable.",
